== Overview ==
The Photonic DV uses a deep set energy grid to provide adequate protection with a very fast recharge. Like the [[Photonic SV Shield|SV]], this model also comes with an attractive stand.

== Where to Acquire ==
The Photonic DV Shield can be bought in the workshop, or found in caves, vaults, and bot remains in Vulcore.
